  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "BIM MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>BIM MANAGER </strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Involve and lead in checking and coordination of drawings and as-built drawings with all respective trades (eg Architectural, Structural, MEP and Specialist Subcontractors works).</li><li>Plan, manage, and oversee the digital delivery process using BIM technologies.</li><li>Coordinate with consultants, contractors, and stakeholders to ensure seamless digital integration.</li><li>Lead and manage the BIM and drafting team to deliver high-quality models and drawings for construction projects.</li><li>Coordinate with project managers, engineers, and consultants to ensure BIM standards and workflows are implemented effectively.</li><li>Oversee model integration, clash detection, and coordination using BIM tools.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 5 years of proven leadership experience managing BIM and drafter teams in the construction industry.</li><li>Possess a BIM certification recognized by BCA (Building and Construction Authority, Singapore).</li><li>Strong proficiency in BIM software (e.g., Revit, Navisworks, AutoCAD, etc.).</li><li>Good understanding of construction processes, coordination, and documentation requirements.</li><li>Demonstrate a reliable, responsive and positive work ethic with the highest degree of integrity.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Suitable candidates are encouraged to apply to this position via Apply Now button or email to <strong>Career@kah.com.sg</strong></p><p><em>Only shortlisted applicants will be notified. </em></p><p><br /></p>",
